New project setup

create standard file structure

index.html (std)
package.json (std)
app/app.component.ts (root component)
app/app.module.ts (root module)
app/main.ts
systemjs.config.js (use std)
.gitignore (std)
gulpfile.js (std)
tsconfig.json (std)

npm install
$ bower init
$ bower install bootstrap --save (this saves bower dependancies so vendor.css and vendor.min.js exist)
